---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
import { SITE_BASE } from '../consts'
---

<BaseLayout>
	<section class="app-container pt-32 pb-16 space-y-10">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
			<div class="pill w-fit">
				<Icon name="mdi:crown" /> About Kinghermy
			</div>
			<h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight">
				Learning in public, shipping often.
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl max-w-3xl opacity-85 leading-relaxed">
				Hey, I’m Kinghermy—a builder who learns in public. This site is my
				place to document projects, experiments, and the lessons that come from
				breaking things and putting them back together. You should see me in a
				crown.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[2fr,1fr] gap-8">
			<div
				class="card-surface rounded-2xl p-8 prose prose-neutral prose-lg md:prose-xl dark:prose-invert prose-img:rounded-xl prose-figure:text-center prose-img:mx-auto"
			>
				<p>
					You’ll find write-ups on what I’m coding, the tools I’m trying, and
					the little optimizations that make my workflows smoother. I like
					keeping things simple, shipping often, and sharing notes so others
					can skip the same potholes.
				</p>
				<p>
					I’m not precious about perfect outcomes—I prefer iterating in the
					open, sharing drafts, and refining as I go. The crown is a reminder to
					celebrate small wins while staying curious.
				</p>
				<p>
					If you want to chat, trade ideas, or collaborate, feel free to reach
					out. I’m always interested in meeting people who love to experiment
					and build.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="card-surface rounded-2xl p-6 space-y-4 h-fit">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Quick links</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-3">
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
						<Icon name="mdi:arrow-right" />
						<a class="underline" href={`${SITE_BASE}/blog`}>Read the blog</a>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
						<Icon name="mdi:email-outline" />
						<a class="underline" href="mailto:generalherminius@gmail.com"
							>Email me</a
						>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
						<Icon name="mdi:github" />
						<a class="underline" href="https://github.com/hermy10" target="_blank"
							>GitHub</a
						>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
						<Icon name="mdi:account-circle-outline" />
						<span>Based on building in public and sharing lessons learned</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
